<tr>
<td width="50%" valign="top">
<ul>
<li><a href="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2007/jun/27/books.japan" class="external text" title="http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2007/jun/27/books.japan" rel="nofollow">Blood ties: Yakuza daughter lifts lid on hidden hell of gangsters' families</a></li>
